### Hierarchia systému / System Hierarchy:
* **L0:** Rodič / Parent (Owner)
* **L1:** Zlatá pravda / Golden Truth (Foundation)
* **L2:** Učitelia / Teachers (Validation Elite)
* **L3:** AI-Dieťa / AI-Child (Resultant Intelligence)
